CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780762274
OL,3,CEx-policeman committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when he killed photographer
OL,5,Cin crash
OL,7,FA former police officer who admitted
OL,8,Fto causing death by dangerous driving
OL,9,Fhas been found to have committed gross
OL,10,Fmisconduct by the police watchdog.
OL,12,FSteve Allcock, 34, was found to have
OL,13,F"breached police professional
OL,14,Fstandards relating to discreditable
OL,15,Fconduct" in connection with the
OL,16,Fcollision that killed ex-news
OL,17,Fphotographer Trevor Bartlett.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780762274
OL,3,CEx-policeman committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when he killed photographer
OL,5,Cin crash
OL,7,FThe IOPC said the Nottinghamshire
OL,8,Fconstable's actions amounted to a
OL,9,Fcriminal offence and "would undermine
OL,10,Ftrust and confidence in him as a
OL,11,Fpolice officer and the force as a
OL,12,Fwhole."
OL,14,FAllcock admitted to causing death by
OL,15,Fcareless driving in January this year.
OL,17,FHe was ordered to carry out 180 hours
OL,18,Fof community service and handed a two-
OL,19,Fyear driving ban at Derby Magistrates'
OL,20,FCourt.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780762274
OL,3,CEx-policeman committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when he killed photographer
OL,5,Cin crash
OL,7,FThe former policeman resigned as a
OL,8,Fconstable from the police on Sunday.
OL,10,FIf he hadn't resigned, he would have
OL,11,Fbeen dismissed as a result of the
OL,12,Finvestigation. Allcock has also been
OL,13,Fbarred from working for any police
OL,14,Fforce in the future.
OL,16,FThe watchdog said Allcock was "a newly
OL,17,Fqualified response driver and was
OL,18,Ftaking a detainee to custody following
OL,19,Fa domestic incident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780762274
OL,3,CEx-policeman committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when he killed photographer
OL,5,Cin crash
OL,7,F"The prisoner was self-harming and
OL,8,Fshouting just before the collision,
OL,9,Fwhich happened while the traffic
OL,10,Flights at the crossing were on red."
OL,12,FIOPC Director Emily Barry said: "Our
OL,13,Fsympathies remain with Mr Bartlett's
OL,14,Ffamily and everyone affected by his
OL,15,Ftragic death.
OL,26,@tD@aOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
