OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780762274
OL,3,CEx-policeman committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when he killed photographer
OL,5,Cin crash
OL,7,F"Police may drive through red lights
OL,8,Fwhere necessary but should not
OL,9,Fendanger the safety of other road
OL,10,Fusers. PC Allcock failed to consider
OL,11,Fthe potential hazards, with fatal
OL,12,Fconsequences, and he has now been held
OL,13,Faccountable for his actions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@]O]
