PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780762274
OL,3,CEx-policeman committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when he killed photographer
OL,5,Cin crash
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the IOPC said, "The
OL,8,FIOPC's investigation was completed in
OL,9,FDecember 2024 when we found a case to
OL,10,Fanswer against the officer for gross
OL,11,Fmisconduct. A file of evidence was
OL,12,Freferred to the Crown Prosecution
OL,13,FService, which authorised the charge
OL,14,Fagainst PC Allcock."
OL,16,FMr Bartlett worked for the Nottingham
OL,17,FPost as a photographer and was
OL,18,Fparticularly well known among
OL,19,FNottingham Forest fans for the photos
OL,20,Fhe took when Brian Clough managed the
OL,21,Fclub.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
